    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, though all major electronics and the air conditioning remain functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but the engine has a minor oil leak and the suspension feels a bit loose, suggesting that some maintenance will be required in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind cosmetic imperfections.",
