    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to a standard rarely seen outside of a showroom floor. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, all protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating applied last season. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the original factory floor mats have been protected by weather-resistant liners since day one. Every electronic feature, from the high-definition infotainment suite to the ambient lighting and climate control, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships, and I have a comprehensive binder containing every service record from the date of purchase. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is free from any debris or surface oxidation. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never been driven in inclement weather. I welcome any third-party pre-purchase inspection to verify its concours-level quality. This is an investment-grade example for a discerning collector or enthusiast.",
      "price": 44900.0,
